title: Myggan
overview: Myggan is a litle known TV producer from Partille who just want to be famous... and rich... and popular with women.... and famous..... and rich..... In his efforts to achieve success Myggan gets involved in the most unlikely events, and he places himself in the most incredible pickles to go with the most handsome pinglan at the party, to get recognition as a television producer and to beat his nemesis Grazzi fingers. Needless to say - he rarely succeeds.
